com.ibm.team.scm.client

Interface IWorkspaceConnection.ISaveOp

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IWorkspaceConnection.IConfigurationOp, IWorkspaceConnection.IMergeResultOp
    Enclosing interface:
    IWorkspaceConnection

    public static interface IWorkspaceConnection.ISaveOp
extends IWorkspaceConnection.IMergeResultOp
    Configuration operation structure which represents saving a new item state in the repository. Instances are manufactured by IWorkspaceConnection.IConfigurationOpFactory, and used in IWorkspaceConnection#commit(IChangeSetHandle, Collection).

    0.6 (RTC 1.0)
